Recommendation system rules.

Primary recommendation model must be trained from scratch.

Preferred models

Random Forest

or

XGBoost

Use

Feature Engineering

Pairwise Similarity Dataset

Model Evaluation

Joblib

Sentence Transformers are allowed ONLY as an optional reranking step after the trained ML model selects the top candidate sneakers.

Do not use embeddings as the primary recommendation engine.

Do not use FAISS because dataset size is small.

Keep inference under 150ms.
